ative Songs|US<br />Alt.]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/music/tash-sultana/chart-history/alternative-songs|title=Tash Sultana Chart History: Alternative Songs|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=1 May 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Higher\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ouvirmusica.com.br/tash-sultana/higher/|title= Higher by Tash Sultana|publisher=Ouvir Musica|date=2015|accessdate=4 December 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2015\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{N/a|Non-album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Brainflower\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/events/tash-sultana-brain-flower-single-launch/416304131911742/|title=TASH SULTANA BRAIN FLOWER SINGLE LAUNCH|publisher=Facebook|date=29 August 2015|accessdate=4 December 2018}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Gemini\"<!-- iTunes links are allowable per [[WP:RS]]: \"inline citations may be allowed to e-commerce pages such as that of [...] an album on its streaming-music page, in order to verify such things as titles\" --><ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/gemini-single/id1105306256|title=Gemini - Single by Tash Sultana on Apple Music|publisher=[[Apple Inc.]]|accessdate=28 January 2017}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2016\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''Notion''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Notion (Tash Sultana song)|Notion]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/notion-single/id1123860808|title=Notion - Single by Tash Sultana on Apple Music|publisher=Apple Inc.|accessdate=28 January 2017}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n* [[ARIA Charts|ARIA]]: Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA2018\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Jungle (Tash Sultana song)|Jungle]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/jungle-single/id1151751011|title=Jungle - Single by Tash Sultana on Apple Music|publisher=Apple Inc.|accessdate=28 January 2017}}</